								<center>
									<b>
										<img src='90002.png' title='Menu'> About
									</b>
								</center>
								<br>
								Tradesman is an online turn-based strategy game focusing on producing, manufacturing and trading. The game focuses on establishing a colony, building production facilities, producing commodities and goods, trading, and managing wealth. The player is presented as the lord of the colony. The main focus of the game is to achieve a high score towards the end of the game (the predefined number of rounds). The land of the colony is defined by a number of square tiles in which building is accessible. Almost all aspects of the game are volatile and change in each round based on the user actions or other factors.
								<br>
								<br>
								The game score is calculated by a combination of statistics during the players reign in the game. The number of citizens, buildings, wealth, as well as other aspects of the gameplay affect the final score.
								<br>
								<br>
								<center>
									<a data-role='none' href='#index'><button class='button_short' title='Manual index'>&nbsp;Manual index&nbsp;</button></a>
