									</b>
								</center>
								<br>
								The game is round-based. Each round, the time clock ticks and increases by one. Each round represent one day in time. The time pane shows the current date as well as how many days will the game last times the minutes per round.
								<br>
								<br>
								The player during the day may build or destroy buildings, buy or sell commodities. By pressing the <img src='70010.png' title='Next'> proceed button, the day is over and a seson summary is presented. Each round can last up to several minutes as predefined before each game. If the player do not proceed to end the round after this time limit, the round ends automatically. During the season summary, the production and all prices are updated. The season summary informs the player about all changes, presents problem on the production line (whether manufactured commodities lack primary commodities in order to produce any), as well as factors concerning citizens, money, productivity and other.
								<br>
								<br>
								The game do not have a save function since it is real time and each action or change is processed immediately. Thus exiting the game do not affect each action applied. The game ends when the predifined number of rounds have passed.
